subject: Attention: Dear Beneficiary
body:
Attention: Dear Beneficiary
This is to bring to your notice that we have credited your total sum of
$5,000,000.00 USD into an ATM VISA card and we have deposited it with DHL
Express Company to deliver it to you. We paid all the necessary charges
such as Company registration and delivery fee.
The only money you will send to them is the security keeping charges of your
ATM VISA card $50.00 dollars.
 We tried to pay that but they complained that
they don't know when you will contact them for the delivery and the demurrage
might have increased by then. I deposited it on 30/01/2024.
Therefore,
 contact
them now with Your:
Your Full Name........
Your Country............
Your City Airport........
Your Home Address........
Telephone Number.........
Gender...................
DHL Express
Agent In Charge
Charles R Brewer
Email address:expressdeliveryd49@gmail.com

subject: Re: Attention: Dear Beneficiary
body:
Hello Charles Brewer,

Thank you for your message. It's quite exciting to hear about the ATM VISA card. I'm curious, how did this come about? And could you please explain a bit more about these security keeping charges?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Frank
